{
  "stem": "2830.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put and-- and-- and that, you know, turned to aluminum.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It hardens.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- my job was to take each sack-- the sacks came in-- and slide them in into a, you, know, and a clean the dust out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Purified the sacks, and you stack the sacks up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my hair and my face, they gave us those blue uniform slacks, and a-- and a thing to wear.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Coat.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was from blue, it went white from that--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--aluminum, from that powder.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My face, every time I needed to see where I put the sack, and I had to wipe to get that dust of my eyes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One day the inspection comes in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said to-- he asked that foreman, whoever it was, the German, how old we are.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, I don't think-- if they're not going to get any protection and masks, for the-- at least for the mouth and nose, that they're not going to survive.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of dust and aluminum dust.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not going to survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So it then took about a week or so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came in with masks just to cover the nose and mouth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the eyes was still-- you were-- then, they gave us a kerchief, you know, for the-- for my head.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that used to go in to take showers after work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't get out that aluminum from your hair.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you rinse and rinse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my eyes-- my vision got, you know, so blurred.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I have to survive this way, that's OK, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got paid for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every week you got paid.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
